UTAH COUNTY RECORDER
2008 Feb 22 2:16 pm FEE 10.00 BY EO
RECORDED FOR TPM INC
NOTICE OF LIEN
TO WHOM IT MAY CONCERN:
Notice is hereby given that Summer Village HOA hereby claims and intends to hold a lien upon certain
land and premises owned or reputed to by owned by Fernanda Eliza Dalrymple located at
1493 North June Street , Saratoga Springs , UT 84045 , and which is legally described as:
Unit 38, Summer Village Condos Phase 2
This lien is to secure the payment of $ 1,435.00 owing to Summer Village HOA as assessment against
said real property.
Said indebtedness represents the expenses assessed against the owner in accordance with the
Homeowners Bylaws, the terms of which the undersigned did hereby agree to abide.
The undersigned holds and claims lien against said real property by virtue of the provisions of Section
20, Chapter 8, Title 57, Utah Code Ann. (1953 as amended), and by virtue of the declaration of the
property referred to above.
Dated this 2/22/2008
Summer Village HOA
